            <h2>Help with the DPL</h2>

            <p>The digital communications team works with colleagues across the University to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>consult on projects that use the DPL</li>
                <li>train developers on the use of existing patterns</li>
                <li>create new patterns.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you would like to use the digital pattern library for your own web project the digital communications team can help.</p>
            <p>Please contact the digital communications team by emailing <a href="mailto:itservicedesk@st-andrews.ac.uk">itservicedesk@st-andrews.ac.uk</a>.</p>

